title: Matt Walsh Revisits His What Is A Woman Interview With Dr. Forcier
description:
Matt Walsh revisits the interview he had with Dr. Forcier during the filming of his documentary What Is A Woman?

Watch my new Daily Wire original documentary “What Is A Woman?” at whatisawoman.com.
